Sentencas: The effects of amount of pore former used to produce porosity in the anode of an anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cell were examined.
Titulo: Effects of the use of pore formers on performance of an anode supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The pore-forming material utilized was rice starch.
Titulo: Effects of the use of pore formers on performance of an anode supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The reduction rate of the anode material was measured by Thermogravimetric analysis to qualitatively characterize the gas transport within the porous anode materials.
Titulo: Effects of the use of pore formers on performance of an anode supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Fuel cells with varying amounts of porosity produced by using rice starch as a pore former were tested.
Titulo: Effects of the use of pore formers on performance of an anode supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The performance of the fuel cell was the greatest with an optimum amount of pore former used to create porosity in the anode.
Titulo: Effects of the use of pore formers on performance of an anode supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This optimum is believed to be related to a trade off between increasing gas diffusion to the active three-phase boundary region of the anode and the loss of performance because of the replacement of active three-phase boundary regions of the anode with porosity.
Titulo: Effects of the use of pore formers on performance of an anode supported solid oxide fuel cell
